<emphasis bold="true" box="[283,519,1904,1928]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Freyastera mortenseni</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Madsen, F. J." box="[533,686,1904,1928]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" pagination="23 - 32" refId="ref47296" refString="Madsen, F. J. (1956) Echinoidea, Asteroidea, and Ophiuroidea from depths exceeding 6000 m. Galathea Reports, 2, 23 - 32." type="journal article" year="1956">Madsen, 1956</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
Scale bar=3.0 mm. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[907,931,1904,1928]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">A.</emphasis>
Whole body-top/lateral view. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1243,1266,1904,1928]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">B.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[1273,1338,1905,1928]" class="Asteroidea" family="Goniasteridae" genus="Iconaster" kingdom="Animalia" order="Valvatida" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Echinodermata" rank="species" species="situ">
<emphasis box="[1273,1338,1905,1928]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">In situ</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
abactinal view showing disk. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[351,375,1940,1964]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">C.</emphasis>
Oral view showing mouth spines. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[722,747,1940,1964]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">D.</emphasis>
Pedicellariae with articulated valves. Scale bar=20 µm 
<emphasis box="[1305,1327,1941,1964]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">E.</emphasis>
Individual valve showing teeth on tip. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[431,450,1976,2000]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">F.</emphasis>
